Mecrisp

Mecrisp is an implementation of a standalone native code Forth for MSP430 microcontrollers. Many chips and all current MSP430 based Launchpads are supported. It fits into 11 kb of flash or fram and runs with at least 512 bytes of ram. You can choose to compile to flash or to ram, and it generates native code with folding, inlining of short words and it
